---
title: Tofu & Veggie Poke Bowl with Toasted Sesame Dressing & Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls, because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses Peking-style tofu, Asian greens, carrot and cucumber, with a nutty sesame dressing to tie the whole thing together.
